column16: other_desc:I used two -- one in first half of game and one in second half of game (approximately and with some played randomly)  i stayed on planet until the number mined was too small to bother going down a few more - did this until about half way i got the feeling i was staying for smaller numbers than the travel time would have cost me so started doing only one dig per planet (more sometimes just on whim).
